I've been in business for over 10 years - I love my job! I work with you and your budget to make you fall in love with your home again. Maybe you just need new paint colours and drapes or maybe you need a wrecking ball; no project is too big or too small!
 Home Staging is essential for getting the most money and the fastest sale of your home. I can give you a customized Action Plan to make your home stand out against the competition. 
Building a new home? Let me help you right from blueprint stage or on moving day, I can sort through the overwhelming details of selections, upgrades that are smart and deadlines so that you are spending your money wisely and ending up with a home you will love for years to come.
